%h1 Remove Link

%p
  Are you sure you want to <strong class="warning">permanently remove</strong> the following search term?

%table.index#search_terms{ :cellpadding => 0, :cellspacing => 0, :border => 0 }
  %tbody
    %tr.node.level-1
      %td.search_term
        = image('twitter_search/search_term', :alt => 'search-term-icon')
        = h @search_term.query

- form_for [:admin, @search_term], :html => {:method => :delete} do
  %p.buttons
    %input.button{ :type => "submit", :value => "Delete Link" }
    or
    = link_to 'Cancel', admin_search_term_url
